snippet.title: SNES Kaizou Choujin Shubibinman Zero
snippet.description:
Support Shiryu on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Shiryu
https://www.facebook.com/ShiryuVideoGames/

NCS's "Kaizou Choujin Shubibinman Zero" for the Satellaview! Now why would I be I making another video of this lovely gem? for the best news ever: "Kaizou Choujin Shubibinman Zero" is getting for the first time ever a SNES physical cartridge release! Read all the details at Nintendo Life. Also remember this is the third game of the "Pulseman" series, with previous games found on PC Engine. If you like "mega Man" you should check out the whole trilogy. Enjoy!

Nintendo Life Post: http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2017/05/columbus_circle_is_releasing_a_new_super_famicom_game_this_year
